high_descs: Turn right and go straight to the wall, then right to exit this room, then left and through the doorway straight ahead, going to the bed.
Pick up the butter knife from the bed.
Leave the room the way you came in, then go straight all the way to the kitchen area, going to the counters on the right.
Slice the onion on the counter.
Turn around to the sink.
Put the knife into the sink.
Turn back to the sliced onion.
Pick up an onion slice.
Turn around to the fridge just ahead.
Cool the onion slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn back to the sink.
Put the onion slice on the counter next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled onion slice on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the knife from the bed.
Turn around and go near the counter top.
Cut the onion into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the butter knife on the sink table.
Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the onion from the counter top.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the onion into the fridge.
Then take it out and go near the sink.
Put the onion on the sink table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the butter knife and onion on the sink table.
